title: #55: Radio Days (Frazer Smith, David Taylor, Ari Shaffir)
itunes:title: Radio Days with Frazer Smith and David Taylor
description: Frazer Smith shares his story of how he went from being a radio god to how he lost it all. It's a really interesting tale. And I had my friend David Taylor cohost with me because he knew a lot of Frazier's stories already and I wanted his help guiding it.
